<p>Lump sum payments are made within 45 days of your policy ending as long as none of your Group has submitted a claim for an event that took place before the end of your policy term. For example, if your policy ends on 3rd March and your Reward Pot
    was worth £48 and none of your Group submits a claim by 31st March, we will payout £48 to you by the 17th April.</p>

<p>Circumstances in which your Reward Pot will not be paid out to you:</p>

